19. Permission Architecture
Permissions are role-based.
Project Manager
Full control.
Backend Engineer
Can only modify assigned features.
Designer
Can edit assigned design deliverables.
QA
Can create reviews.
Organization Admin
Can monitor every project.
No complicated permission builder is needed for an internal tool.

